text: Kurt-Yelga () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Mrakovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 40 as of 2010. There are 15 streets. == Geography == It is located 4 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Kurt-Yelga
